data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Priced to sell this craftsman home is perfect for first time homebuyers! Update it to your own satisfaction. This 3-bedroom 1 bath home is ready for new owners to add their own personal touches to it. Two bedrooms upstairs and one bedroom off of the kitchen. Restroom is on the main floor. Fully fenced backyard with a gate. Great home with character not found in new homes. Brand new roof is a couple months old.
